OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FA lodger who killed his 80-year old
OL,8,F'best friend' landlord after slapping
OL,9,Fhim at his Worthing flat has been
OL,10,Fjailed for more than two years.
OL,12,FArno Engels' assault on Anthony
OL,13,FScarrott caused him to fall to the
OL,14,Ffloor and hit his head on 11 September
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FScarrott died in intensive care at the
OL,18,FRoyal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,19,FBrighton three days later.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
