CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FToday at Hove Crown Court, Engels was
OL,8,Fsentenced to two years and four months
OL,9,Ffor manslaughter - he will serve up to
OL,10,Fhalf in custody and the for the rest
OL,11,Fof his sentence he will be released on
OL,12,Flicence.
OL,14,FA well-known figure who worked at a
OL,15,Fpub in the area, Mr Scarrott was
OL,16,Fdescribed by his family as a 'happy go
OL,17,Flucky gregariously generous' gentlemen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
