OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FEngels, a South African national from
OL,8,FNamibia, who arrived in the UK 18
OL,9,Fmonths before the fatal assault, had
OL,10,Fcome across the pensioner on the floor
OL,11,Flaying outside a pub.
OL,13,FGrateful for his help, the class A-
OL,14,Fdrug addict was then offered a room by
OL,15,FMr Scarrott for #400 a month, it's
OL,16,Ffrom here those who knew him said
OL,17,Fcontact became sporadic as Engels took
OL,18,Fcontrol of his life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
