FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FFriends described his increasing
OL,8,Fabsence in replying to calls, and
OL,9,Fthere was concerns he was a victim of
OL,10,Fcuckooing. He'd also been spotted
OL,11,Fmultiple times with injuries including
OL,12,Fblack eyes and ended up in hospital.
OL,14,FProsecutors say there was a mutual use
OL,15,Fof alcohol and Mr Engels encouraged a
OL,16,Fshared taking of cocaine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
