CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FWhen he was first arrested Engels gave
OL,8,Fa false account but during questioning
OL,9,Ffollowing Mr Scartott's death, he told
OL,10,Fpolice, 'Mr Scarrott was the best mate
OL,11,Fin the world, I want to come clean. I
OL,12,Ftold police I pushed him but I slapped
OL,13,Fhim'.
OL,15,FA statement from Mr Scarrott's sister
OL,16,FSandra Scarrott was read out in court.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
