FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FShe wrote, "Losing my brother Tony, or
OL,8,Fmy bruv as I liked to call him, has
OL,9,Fnot been easy but the loss of someone
OL,10,Fyou hold dear never is but it
OL,11,Fhappening like this is horrible.
OL,13,F"I haven't been sleeping, this has
OL,14,Fbeen getting worse in recent weeks,
OL,15,Fthere is always something on my mind.
OL,16,FI know everyone has good intentions
OL,17,Fbut my days are filled with calls over
OL,18,FTony's death. I don't get a minute's
OL,19,Fpeace and it is difficult to grieve
OL,20,Fnormally.
OL,26,@oD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
