OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,F"Myself and those closest to Tony have
OL,8,Fhad to wait for four months to have a
OL,9,Ffuneral owing to this being a criminal
OL,10,Finvestigation there was a delay in
OL,11,Freleasing his body.
OL,13,F"You hear of an 80 year old dying and
OL,14,Fit conjures up images of an elderly
OL,15,Fand frail person. On his 80th
OL,16,Fbirthday, Tony went abseiling and jet
OL,17,Fskiing in Spain.
OL,19,F"Tony was a kind generous person who
OL,20,Fwould always take people in who've
OL,21,Ffallen through hard times.
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
