OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777554669
OL,3,CLodger who slapped landlord, 80, who
OL,4,Cfell and died, is jailed for
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,F"I fear this generous, loving nature
OL,8,Fmade Tony vulnerable to being taken
OL,9,Fadvantage of and I have no doubt Arno
OL,10,Ftook advantage of this and it angers
OL,11,Fme his kindness would have been
OL,12,Fexploited as it has.
OL,14,F"It's desperately sad his life ended
OL,15,Fin the way it did."
OL,17,FFollowing sentencing at Hove Crown
OL,18,FCourt Arno Engels now faces
OL,19,Fdeportation.
OL,26,@wD@SO]
